OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,FA former Labour local authority mayor
OL,7,Fand an ex-councillor have joined
OL,8,FReform UK, accusing the ruling party
OL,9,Fof failing London.
OL,11,FSir Robin Wales, who was directly
OL,12,Felected mayor of Newham from 2002 to
OL,13,F2018, and Clive Furness, who served on
OL,14,Fthe council, announced they were
OL,15,Fswitching to Nigel Farage's party on
OL,16,FWednesday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
