PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,FThe Reform UK leader had teased the
OL,7,Fprospect of a Labour recruit weeks
OL,8,Fago, saying there were talks ongoing
OL,9,Fwith a number of people who had held
OL,10,F"senior positions" in the party and
OL,11,F"they will come".
OL,13,FMr Furness has been selected as
OL,14,FReform's candidate for mayor of Newham
OL,15,Fwhile Sir Robin will act as the
OL,16,Fparty's London director of local
OL,17,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@RO]sD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
