CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,FLondon Labour suggested Reform was
OL,7,F"scraping the barrel" as neither man
OL,8,Fhad been involved in the Labour
OL,9,Fmovement "for some time". Sir Robin
OL,10,Fwas deselected by the party in Newham
OL,11,Fin 2018.
OL,13,FAnnouncing his move at a press
OL,14,Fconference with Mr Farage on
OL,15,FWednesday, Sir Robin said Reform had
OL,16,F"a lot of rough edges" but represented
OL,17,Fa chance to "transform our society".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]qD@JOUqD@XO]xD@AOUxD@VO]yD@
OL,26,AMOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
