OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,FHe accused Labour of having abandoned
OL,7,Fits roots and said that under London
OL,8,FMayor Sir Sadiq Khan the capital had
OL,9,Fseen "soaring crime, failing services,
OL,10,Fand a party that prioritises the
OL,11,Fwealthy elite over the working class
OL,12,Fit was built to represent".
OL,14,FHe defended Reform, which Labour has
OL,15,Faccused of peddling divisive politics,
OL,16,Ftelling the event: "If I thought
OL,17,FReform was racist, if Clive thought
OL,18,FReform is racist, we wouldn't be in
OL,19,Fthis room or even near this
OL,20,Fheadquarters.
OL,26,@qD@FOUtD@ZO]xD@TOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
