PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,FIt's not and I challenge anybody to
OL,7,Fshow how it is."
OL,9,FMr Furness said there had been a
OL,10,F"Balkanisation of Britain", with
OL,11,Fpeople voting on religious and racial
OL,12,Flines, which he cited among the
OL,13,Fconcerns which had led him to join
OL,14,FReform.
OL,16,FHe said: "Labour has clearly and
OL,17,Fdemonstrably failed London.
OL,26,@oD@PO]rD@AOUrD@ZO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
