PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,F"It's sad to see that even Newham, a
OL,7,Fborough that Sir Robin and I managed
OL,8,Fto lift out of deprivation, has gone
OL,9,Fcompletely backwards under a Labour
OL,10,Fmayor and a Labour council that is now
OL,11,Fcompletely out of touch with the
OL,12,Fcommunities it was meant to represent."
OL,14,FAsked whether Sir Robin and Mr Furness
OL,15,Fwere the Labour figures who Mr Farage
OL,16,Fhad spoken of when he hinted at a
OL,17,Fdefection earlier this year, the
OL,18,FReform leader suggested there would be
OL,19,Fmore.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
