OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,F"They're some of them ` we are talking
OL,7,Fto a number of Labour figures," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"What is particularly pertinent about
OL,11,Fthese two guys is their record in
OL,12,Fgovernment in London as we approach a
OL,13,FLondon election.
OL,15,F"There are other Labour figures we're
OL,16,Ftalking to, and you will see them over
OL,17,Fthe course of the next weeks and
OL,18,Fmonths."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]rD@AOUwD@AOUzD@HO]
