OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,FUnder Sir Robin's leadership, Newham
OL,7,Fwas at the heart of the regeneration
OL,8,Fassociated with the 2012 Summer
OL,9,FOlympics.
OL,11,FHe was was heavily involved in
OL,12,FLondon's Olympic delivery and legacy,
OL,13,Fincluding roles on the London
OL,14,FOrganising Committee and the Olympic
OL,15,FPark Legacy Company, championing
OL,16,Fefforts to ensure residents benefited
OL,17,Ffrom jobs and development linked to
OL,18,Fthe Games.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
