OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,FDuring his time on the council, he was
OL,7,Fa mayoral adviser working on issues
OL,8,Frelated to social care and community
OL,9,Fwellbeing, and was part of the mayoral
OL,10,Fexecutive under successive
OL,11,Fadministrations.
OL,13,FA London Labour spokesperson said: "If
OL,14,FClive Furness and Robin Wales count as
OL,15,Fa 'major London announcement', Reform
OL,16,Freally are scraping the barrel.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
