PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,F"Neither man has been part of the
OL,7,FLabour movement for some time. In
OL,8,FNewham, Robin Wales was removed by
OL,9,Flocal members following concerns about
OL,10,Fhis record in office after Labour
OL,11,Fmembers selected a new candidate.
OL,13,F"Nigel Farage, Laila Cunningham and
OL,14,Ftheir allies spend their time talking
OL,15,FLondon down and attacking the success
OL,16,Fof one of the most proudly
OL,17,Fmulticultural cities in the world.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
