OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772644277
OL,3,CTwo former senior Labour figures in
OL,4,CLondon politics join Reform UK
OL,6,F"Meanwhile, Labour is focused on
OL,7,Fdelivering for London ` supporting
OL,8,F240,000 children by ending the two-
OL,9,Fchild cap, cutting energy bills for
OL,10,F3.7 million households, expanding free
OL,11,Fschool meals and breakfast clubs, and
OL,12,Fstrengthening protections for 2.7
OL,13,Fmillion renters.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
